 size, enhancement, Bosniak class, etc.)\n- Help you prepare focused questions for a urologist/radiologist\n\nIf you share the **actual report text** (or clear scan screenshots), I can help interpret it in plain language.  \nIf this is about real symptoms (e.g., blood in urine, persistent flank pain, unexplained weight loss), please seek medical care promptly.","textSignature":"msg_00afefed00d56ac90169aaf760fab8819187c55f175aa78d5d"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":40546,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40795,"cost":{"input":0.0709555,"output":0.003486,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07444150000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772812125726}}
